node.title: One dead, another critical in Mount Maunganui incident
node.description: The incident occurred at 8:01am on Tuesday.
node.content: ["Police and ambulance staff are responding to a \"sudden death\" incident in Mount Maunganui that also left another person in a critical condition.", "\"Police are assisting Ambulance and Fire Emergency with a sudden death at a Mount Maunganui address,\" a police spokesperson told Newshub.", "A St John spokesperson told Newshub they responded to the incident with one ambulance and one rapid response unit.\u00a0", "\"We were notified of the incident at 08:01,\" a St John spokesperson said.\u00a0", "\"We have assessed and transported one patient in a critical condition to Tauranga Hospital.\"\u00a0"]
